<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Exterior Cleaning Software</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    /* ===== <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Exterior Cleaning Software ===== */

    .ex-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-secondary: #f97316;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      --radius-md: 16px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16);

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 80px;
    }

    .ex-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .ex-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */

    .ex-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .ex-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .ex-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.11em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .ex-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .ex-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 42px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .ex-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .ex-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .ex-hero-tagline {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .ex-hero-ctas {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .ex-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition:
        transform 0.12s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        background 0.15s ease,
        border-color 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .ex-btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.45);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .ex-btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.65);
    }

    .ex-btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.8);
    }

    .ex-btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .ex-hero-trust {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .ex-hero-trust strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .ex-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.06);
      color: #4b5563;
      border: 1px solid rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    /* Hero right: schedule / route card */

    .ex-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .ex-schedule-card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 360px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      background: #0b1020;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 16px 16px 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ex-schedule-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.9), transparent 65%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ex-schedule-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-header-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .ex-schedule-header-title span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .ex-schedule-filter {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-list {
      margin-top: 6px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96);
      padding: 8px 10px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.8fr 0.7fr;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 4px 0;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-row + .ex-schedule-row {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
      margin-top: 3px;
      padding-top: 5px;
    }

    .ex-schedule-row strong {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .ex-status-pill {
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ex-status-pill.scheduled {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
      color: #bfdbfe;
    }

    .ex-status-pill.in-progress {
      background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.25);
      color: #bbf7d0;
    }

    .ex-status-pill.completed {
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25);
      color: #c7d2fe;
    }

    .ex-schedule-footer {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
    }

    .ex-schedule-footer strong {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- SECTION LAYOUT ---------- */

    .ex-section {
      margin-bottom: 52px;
    }

    .ex-section-header {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .ex-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .ex-section-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .ex-section-lead {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .ex-section-lead strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .ex-body-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .ex-body-text p {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .ex-body-text p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* ---------- FEATURES GRID ---------- */

    .ex-feature-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .ex-feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .ex-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .ex-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .ex-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ex-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .ex-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .ex-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .ex-feature-pill {
      margin-top: 4px;
      align-self: flex-start;
      padding: 4px 9px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    /* ---------- RESOURCES / ARTICLES ---------- */

    .ex-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .ex-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .ex-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .ex-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .ex-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .ex-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ex-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .ex-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .ex-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .ex-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- TESTIMONIALS ---------- */

    .ex-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .ex-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .ex-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0.95;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-quote {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-quote em {
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-name {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .ex-testimonial-name strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="ex-page" id="exterior-cleaning-software">
  <div class="ex-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="ex-hero">
      <div>

        <h1 class="ex-title">
          Streamline your <span>exterior cleaning business</span> with <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.
        </h1>

        <p class="ex-sub">
          Running an exterior cleaning business means juggling jobs, teams, vehicles, payments and
          communication – often while you’re out on-site. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> brings it all together in one place so
          you can work smarter, not harder.
        </p>

        <p class="ex-hero-tagline">
          The scheduling, invoicing and payments platform designed for pressure washing, soft washing and
          exterior cleaning companies.
        </p>

        <div class="ex-hero-ctas">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="ex-btn ex-btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="ex-btn ex-btn-secondary">Which plan?</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ex-hero-trust">
          <strong><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> takes care of the admin so you can focus on the work.</strong>
          <span class="ex-pill">Built for field teams · Works on any device</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero media: exterior job schedule -->
      <div class="ex-hero-media">
        <div class="ex-schedule-card">
          <div class="ex-schedule-inner">
            <div class="ex-schedule-header">
              <div class="ex-schedule-header-title">
                Today · Exterior Cleaning
                <span>8 jobs · 2 crews</span>
              </div>
              <div class="ex-schedule-filter">View by crew</div>
            </div>

            <div class="ex-schedule-list">
              <div class="ex-schedule-row">
                <div><strong>Retail Park · Pressure wash</strong></div>
                <div>08:30 → 10:30</div>
                <div><div class="ex-status-pill in-progress">In progress</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="ex-schedule-row">
                <div>Townhouses · Soft wash fronts</div>
                <div>11:00 → 13:00</div>
                <div><div class="ex-status-pill scheduled">Scheduled</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="ex-schedule-row">
                <div>Apartment block · Cladding clean</div>
                <div>14:00 → 17:00</div>
                <div><div class="ex-status-pill completed">Completed</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ex-schedule-footer">
              <span>Send reminders to afternoon customers</span>
              <span><strong>Invoices &amp; payment links</strong> sent automatically</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO COPY -->
    <section class="ex-section">
      <div class="ex-section-header">
        <p class="ex-section-kicker">For exterior cleaning companies</p>
        <h2 class="ex-section-title">Your exterior cleaning jobs planned, organised and in one place.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ex-body-text">
        <p>
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> gives you everything you need to keep your exterior cleaning business running smoothly.
          Book jobs, allocate crews, add notes and photos, and keep customers updated at every stage –
          without relying on paper diaries or scattered messages.
        </p>
        <p>
          Plan your day with drag-and-drop scheduling, then automatically send appointment reminders so
          customers are ready when you arrive. When the job is complete, mark it done in the app to trigger
          invoicing and payment requests.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you’re pressure washing driveways, cleaning roofs and gutters, or taking on large
          commercial exteriors, <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> scales with you – from solo operators to multi-van teams.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <section class="ex-section">
      <div class="ex-section-header">
        <p class="ex-section-kicker">Features</p>
        <h2 class="ex-section-title">Features you’ll love.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="ex-feature-intro">
        <p>
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> is designed to automate your processes and keep admin time to a minimum. It’s easy for
          your crews to use on any mobile device, with real-time updates so office staff can keep on top
          of daily work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ex-feature-grid">
        <!-- Effortless job scheduling -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Job scheduling</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Effortless job scheduling</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            Plan and adjust jobs using a clear visual planner. Quickly move work between crews, reschedule
            due to weather and keep recurring maintenance cleans organised so nothing gets missed.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Drag, drop, done</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Automated invoicing & payments -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Invoicing &amp; payments</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Automated invoicing &amp; payments</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            Create and send invoices in seconds when a job is marked complete. Track who has paid, who
            still owes and send polite reminders – without manually chasing every single job.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Get paid faster</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Route management -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Route management</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Route management &amp; optimisation</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            Assign jobs to specific vehicles or teams, then optimise routes to reduce drive time and fuel
            costs. Crews can navigate directly from the app and update job status as they go.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Less driving, more cleaning</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Customer management -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Customer management</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Customer management</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            Store all your customer details in one place – property information, access notes, past work,
            photos and price history – so any crew member can arrive fully prepared.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Every detail recorded</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Appointment reminders -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Messaging</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Appointment reminders</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            Cut down on no-shows and last-minute cancellations by sending SMS and email reminders at just
            the right time. Keep customers informed about arrival windows, weather delays and follow-up
            visits.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Fewer wasted visits</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Real-time progress -->
        <article class="ex-feature-card">
          <p class="ex-feature-label">Live tracking</p>
          <h3 class="ex-feature-title">Real-time progress tracking</h3>
          <p class="ex-feature-text">
            See which jobs are not started, in progress or complete across all your crews in real time.
            Spot delays early, reassign work and keep customers updated with accurate ETAs.
          </p>
          <div class="ex-feature-pill">Stay one step ahead</div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="ex-section">
      <div class="ex-section-header">
        <p class="ex-section-kicker">What our customers say</p>
        <h2 class="ex-section-title">See how exterior cleaners use <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ex-testimonial-grid">
        <article class="ex-testimonial-card">
          <div class="ex-testimonial-inner">
            <p class="ex-testimonial-tag">Admin &amp; growth</p>
            <p class="ex-testimonial-quote">
              <em>“<%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> has evolved into the control centre of our business.”</em> We plan and re-plan
              jobs, send invoices and track payments all in one place. Any device, any time – it’s
              essential for any appointment-based exterior cleaning company.
            </p>
            <p class="ex-testimonial-name">
              <strong>Service business owner</strong>
              Exterior cleaning &amp; pressure washing
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ex-testimonial-card">
          <div class="ex-testimonial-inner">
            <p class="ex-testimonial-tag">Work-life balance</p>
            <p class="ex-testimonial-quote">
              “Before <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> we were using paper diaries and chasing payments manually. Now reminders,
              invoices and payment links are sent automatically when work is completed. We’ve cut down on
              admin and late payments – and evenings are finally free again.”
            </p>
            <p class="ex-testimonial-name">
              <strong>Owner-operator</strong>
              Exterior cleaning &amp; soft washing
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RESOURCES / ARTICLES -->
    <section class="ex-section">
      <div class="ex-section-header">
        <p class="ex-section-kicker">Resources</p>
        <h2 class="ex-section-title">Useful resources for exterior cleaning businesses.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ex-articles-grid">
        <article class="ex-article-card">
          <p class="ex-article-tag">Customer story</p>
          <h3 class="ex-article-title">How software helped an exterior cleaner grow faster</h3>
          <p class="ex-article-text">
            Follow an exterior cleaning business as they move from paper admin to an all-in-one platform
            for scheduling, invoicing and payments – and the impact it had on their growth.
          </p>
          <p class="ex-article-meta">Reading time · 6 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="ex-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ex-article-card">
          <p class="ex-article-tag">How-to</p>
          <h3 class="ex-article-title">Building repeat exterior cleaning schedules</h3>
          <p class="ex-article-text">
            Learn how to set up recurring maintenance cleans, manage seasonal work and keep track of long
            term exterior cleaning contracts inside <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.
          </p>
          <p class="ex-article-meta">Reading time · 5 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="ex-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ex-article-card">
          <p class="ex-article-tag">Growth</p>
          <h3 class="ex-article-title">Marketing ideas for exterior cleaning companies</h3>
          <p class="ex-article-text">
            Practical ideas for keeping your calendar full – from seasonal campaigns and referral offers
            to using <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>’s messaging tools to stay in touch with customers.
          </p>
          <p class="ex-article-meta">Reading time · 7 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="ex-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>
      </div>
